column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) as objId FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) IS NOT NULL EXEC spExecuteSQL &&&'&&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&&&& as objID, p.ra, p.dec, dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type, p.modelMag_r, s.specObjID, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberID, s.z, s.snMedian FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN PhotoTag p ON p.objID = x.objID JOIN SpecObj s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID ORDER by x.up_id &&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
